_sText:
----------------------------------------------------

De Dust4 Pro.

Follow up to de_dust2, 
with a military feel.


Map created by Gozemem.

Map edited by Robtronic.

----------------------------------------------------

Objectives:

Terrorists: Infiltrate the military 
base and destroy the APCs. 

Counter-terrorists: ALERT! Defend 
the base against attack. Don't 
forget bombsite C.

----------------------------------------------------

Of technical interest:
I have never seen a map with a third bombsite,
though there is support in the game for it. 
There may be a good reason for this,
but it seems to play OK. Have fun.

----------------------------------------------------

The nav file for bots is contained 
inside the BSP using Pakrat.

----------------------------------------------------
